metadata.name: NO CEILINGS 2023
metadata.description:
No Ceilings is a piece depicting my come-up where I let go of fear, elevating me to walk by faith and not by sight alone.

Step outside the box, in everyway possible. The stars are yet another checkpoint on your roadmap to infinity. Your only limitations are the ones you place upon yourself.

Remember, you are the star of your internal reality, woven into the one universal matrix we are all simultaneously creating together. All is one, everything is everything, there is nothing new under the sun. 

Gm! And in case I donâ€™t see ya;  Ga, Ge and Gn.
